e in. Sprinkle with slivered almonds and extra caster sugar."},{"content":"Bake for 20 minutes (160°C). Increase oven temperature to 180°C and bake for 20-25 minutes (180°C), or until a wooden skewer inserted into the centre of the cakes comes out clean. Serve cakes warm."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Granny Smith and Golden Delicious apples work well in this recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 10m","16 portions"]}